name: 70 6k 9k 101
description:
I fed an AI with my Augmented Klecksography Paintings, the so called PREMATURE artworks.
The digital metamorphosis leads to the creation of a new kind of textures and aesthetic, a PREMATURE FLESH birth from what it once was acrylic augmented by digital photography.

This frame has been taken from the Style GAN2 training at the following parameters:

Data set: Selection of 70 PREMATURE artworks
Session Training Steps-Hours: 6000 - 6
Overall Training Steps-Hours: 9000 - 9

101 is the number I gave to the selected frame.

This piece is part of the PREMATURE NFTs installation presented at Funkhaus Berlin for Signals Festival on October 15th-16th 2021.
